data.description: Nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac, this home is an oasis of comfort. It is invitingly spacious and boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.75 bathrooms, a large family room, and gorgeous hardwood flooring - there's something for everyone! Enjoy the outdoors on your 10,000 sq/ft + lot, which is thoughtfully landscaped to perfection, featuring numerous fruit trees alongside a beautiful rock planter, ensuring added greenery or colorful blooms throughout the year. Make dinner parties even more appealing with stainless steel appliances protruding from the kitchen island equipped with a granite countertop. The main suite provides ample space accompanied by a luxurious dual vanity shower/soaking tub combo topped off with a walk-in closet ready for endless outfit ideas! A three-car garage further extends convenience features outfitted with epoxy floors + a sliding door into the back yard where you can take full advantage of all life has to offer. To top this paradise off, you have a newer built pool and spa.
